doc.previous: In December 2010 the Portuguese Wikipedia overtook the Dutch language Wikipedia in number of articles but in the first quarter of 2011 it was surpassed by the Russian and Dutch language Wikipedias ranking in the tenth position It is currently 2015 the 14th Wikipedia version by number of articles
doc.after: The Portuguese language Wikipedia is different from the English one in a number of aspects
